description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 1.2 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Commercial Steam Cookers that are effective as of August 1, 2003. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at  http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=steamcookers.pr_crit_steamcookers
